#: ../../source/base-storage-api-v2.rst:4
msgid "Storage API V2"
msgstr "Storage API V2"

#: ../../source/base-storage-api-v2.rst:6
msgid ""
"MaxCompute Storage API V2 是 MaxCompute 提供的高吞吐数据读写接口。相比于基于 Tunnel 的数据通道， "
"Storage API V2 提供了更细粒度的会话管理、支持 Arrow 格式和 Blob 格式读写、支持增量读取以及表预览等功能， "
"适用于大规模并行数据读写场景。"
msgstr ""
"MaxCompute Storage API V2 is a high-throughput data read/write interface "
"provided by MaxCompute. Compared to the Tunnel-based data channel, "
"Storage API V2 offers finer-grained session management, support for Arrow"
" and Blob format read/write, incremental reading, and table preview, "
"making it suitable for large-scale parallel data read/write scenarios."

#: ../../source/base-storage-api-v2.rst:12
msgid "Storage API V2 需要服务端支持，请确保 MaxCompute 集群已开启相关功能。"
msgstr ""
"Storage API V2 requires server-side support. Make sure the relevant "
"features are enabled on your MaxCompute cluster."

#: ../../source/base-storage-api-v2.rst:15
msgid "基本概念"
msgstr "Core concepts"

#: ../../source/base-storage-api-v2.rst:17
msgid "Storage API V2 的核心概念包括："
msgstr "The core concepts of Storage API V2 include:"

#: ../../source/base-storage-api-v2.rst:19
msgid "**会话（Session）**：读写操作的事务上下文。读会话管理数据分片，写会话保证数据原子性。"
msgstr ""
"**Session**: The transactional context for read/write operations. A read "
"session manages data splits, while a write session ensures data "
"atomicity."

#: ../../source/base-storage-api-v2.rst:20
msgid "**分片（Split）**：读会话将数据按大小、并行度等方式分为多个分片，每个分片可独立读取，支持并行处理。"
msgstr ""
"**Split**: A read session divides data into multiple splits by size, "
"parallelism, etc. Each split can be read independently, enabling parallel"
" processing."

#: ../../source/base-storage-api-v2.rst:21
msgid "**流（Stream）**：写会话中的数据上传通道。一个写会话可创建多个流以支持并行写入。"
msgstr ""
"**Stream**: A data upload channel within a write session. A write session"
" can create multiple streams to support parallel writes."

#: ../../source/base-storage-api-v2.rst:22
msgid "**压缩（Compression）**：支持 UNCOMPRESSED（默认）、LZ4 和 ZSTD 压缩算法，减少网络传输数据量。"
msgstr ""
"**Compression**: Supports UNCOMPRESSED (default), LZ4, and ZSTD "
"compression algorithms to reduce network data transfer."

#: ../../source/base-storage-api-v2.rst:23
msgid "**路由令牌（Route Token）**：服务端返回的路由标识，用于会话亲和性，确保后续请求路由到同一节点。"
msgstr "**Route Token**: A routing identifier returned by the server, used for session affinity to ensure subsequent requests are routed to the same node."

#: ../../source/base-storage-api-v2.rst:24
msgid "**Exactly-Once 模式**：写流支持精确一次语义，通过 access_token 和 row_offset 实现幂等写入。"
msgstr "**Exactly-Once Mode**: Write streams support exactly-once semantics, achieving idempotent writes via access_token and row_offset."

#: ../../source/base-storage-api-v2.rst:27
msgid "客户端初始化"
msgstr "Client initialization"

#: ../../source/base-storage-api-v2.rst:29
msgid ""
"使用 Storage API V2 需要创建 ``StorageApiClient`` 或 ``StorageApiArrowClient`` "
"实例。 两者均需要传入 ODPS 入口对象和表对象（或 Instance 对象）。"
msgstr ""
"To use Storage API V2, you need to create a ``StorageApiClient`` or "
"``StorageApiArrowClient`` instance. Both require an ODPS entry object and"
" a table (or Instance) object."

#: ../../source/base-storage-api-v2.rst:32
msgid ""
"from odps import ODPS\n"
"from odps.apis.storage_api_v2 import StorageApiClient, "
"StorageApiArrowClient\n"
"\n"
"# 初始化 ODPS 入口对象\n"
"odps = ODPS(\n"
"    access_id=\"your_access_id\",\n"
"    secret_access_key=\"your_secret_access_key\",\n"
"    project=\"your_project\",\n"
"    endpoint=\"your_endpoint\",\n"
")\n"
"\n"
"# 获取表对象\n"
"table = odps.get_table(\"your_table\")\n"
"\n"
"# 创建基础客户端（返回原始字节流）\n"
"client = StorageApiClient(odps, table)\n"
"\n"
"# 创建 Arrow 客户端（返回 Arrow RecordBatch，推荐）\n"
"arrow_client = StorageApiArrowClient(odps, table)"
msgstr ""
"from odps import ODPS\n"
"from odps.apis.storage_api_v2 import StorageApiClient, "
"StorageApiArrowClient\n"
"\n"
"# Initialize the ODPS entry object\n"
"odps = ODPS(\n"
"    access_id=\"your_access_id\",\n"
"    secret_access_key=\"your_secret_access_key\",\n"
"    project=\"your_project\",\n"
"    endpoint=\"your_endpoint\",\n"
")\n"
"\n"
"# Get the table object\n"
"table = odps.get_table(\"your_table\")\n"
"\n"
"# Create the base client (returns raw byte streams)\n"
"client = StorageApiClient(odps, table)\n"
"\n"
"# Create the Arrow client (returns Arrow RecordBatches, recommended)\n"
"arrow_client = StorageApiArrowClient(odps, table)"

#: ../../source/base-storage-api-v2.rst:54
msgid ""
"``StorageApiArrowClient`` 继承自 ``StorageApiClient``，额外提供了 "
"``read_rows_arrow``、 ``write_rows_arrow`` 和 ``preview_table_arrow`` "
"方法，能够直接读写 PyArrow RecordBatch 对象， 便于与 pandas 等数据处理框架配合使用。大多数场景下推荐使用 "
"``StorageApiArrowClient``。"
msgstr ""
"``StorageApiArrowClient`` inherits from ``StorageApiClient`` and provides"
" additional ``read_rows_arrow``, ``write_rows_arrow``, and "
"``preview_table_arrow`` methods that directly read/write PyArrow "
"RecordBatch objects, making it easy to integrate with pandas and other "
"data processing frameworks. ``StorageApiArrowClient`` is recommended for "
"most use cases."

#: ../../source/base-storage-api-v2.rst:58
msgid "也可以通过指定 ``quota_name`` 和 ``rest_endpoint`` 参数来使用指定配额和自定义端点："
msgstr ""
"You can also specify ``quota_name`` and ``rest_endpoint`` parameters to "
"use a specific quota and custom endpoint:"

#: ../../source/base-storage-api-v2.rst:60
msgid ""
"client = StorageApiArrowClient(\n"
"    odps, table,\n"
"    quota_name=\"your_quota\",\n"
"    rest_endpoint=\"https://your-custom-endpoint\",\n"
")"
msgstr ""
"client = StorageApiArrowClient(\n"
"    odps, table,\n"
"    quota_name=\"your_quota\",\n"
"    rest_endpoint=\"https://your-custom-endpoint\",\n"
")"

#: ../../source/base-storage-api-v2.rst:68
msgid "还可以通过 ``tags`` 参数设置请求标签："
msgstr "You can also set request tags via the ``tags`` parameter:"

#: ../../source/base-storage-api-v2.rst:70
msgid ""
"client = StorageApiArrowClient(\n"
"    odps, table,\n"
"    tags=\"tag1,tag2\",\n"
")"
msgstr ""
"client = StorageApiArrowClient(\n"
"    odps, table,\n"
"    tags=\"tag1,tag2\",\n"
")"

#: ../../source/base-storage-api-v2.rst:78
msgid "读取数据"
msgstr "Reading data"

#: ../../source/base-storage-api-v2.rst:81
msgid "完整读取流程"
msgstr "Complete read workflow"

#: ../../source/base-storage-api-v2.rst:83
msgid "使用 Storage API V2 读取数据需要以下步骤："
